OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy in the morning with some
OL,6,Fpatchy rain. Mainly dry in the
OL,7,Fafternoon with a few brighter spells
OL,8,Fin the south, but still a little rain
OL,9,Facross Argyll.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FMostly cloudy with a little
OL,12,Frain at times, especially over Argyll.
OL,13,FSome drier spells too, the odd clear
OL,14,Finterval in the east.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FCloudy with some mostly light
OL,17,Frain at times, though with some drier
OL,18,Fspells too. Some heavier rain later in
OL,19,Fthe evening, with strong winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
